				</h4>

				<hr>

				<h3 class="text-center">Revenues:</h3>
				<h4 class="text-center">
					<p>If the revenue does not cover all contributions, the pay-outs for the expenses are given priority, followed by rental fees and working hours.</p>
				</h4>

